{"lemma":"ظَبْيَيْ","slug":"ظَبْيَيْ","root":"ظ.ب.#","root_slug":"ظ-ب-_","root_link":"/words/roots/ظ-ب-_","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":2,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":4},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n27509","n27511"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B8%D9%8E%D8%A8%D9%92%D9%8A%D9%8E%D9%8A%D9%92"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"gazelle, mountain goat, antelope"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"mark by branding"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"name of a star"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"plural of ظَبْي (ẓaby)","tags":["form-of","plural"]}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"From Proto-Semitic *θ̣aby-. Compare Aramaic טַבְיָא (ṭaḇyā), Classical Syriac ܛܒܝܐ (ṭaḇyā), Hebrew צְבִי (ts'ví, ṣəḇī), Ugaritic 𐎑𐎁𐎊 (ẓby)."},"ipa":["/ðˤabj/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n27509","headword_ar":"ظَبْىٌ","root":"ZbY","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A certain animal,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"well known;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb, K, TA;) the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gazaAl","text_ar":"غَزَال"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"gazelle;"},{"kind":"text","text":"to which the former word is applied when used unrestrictedly, and which is app. here meant by the latter word, though this seems properly to signify “ a young gazelle ”]; (M;) [it is the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"gazella dorcas,"},{"kind":"text","text":"also called"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"antilope dorcas,"},{"kind":"text","text":"of which the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ariel,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"antilope Arabica,"},{"kind":"text","text":"is said to be a variety; or, accord. to some, each is a distinct species of gazelle: the name seems to be properly, but not always (as is shown by an explanation of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"riy^omN","text_ar":"رِيْمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"), applied only to the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"true antelope"},{"kind":"text","text":"of Arabia and adjacent countries,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"as distinguished from the cervine and bovine antelopes:"},{"kind":"text","text":"] it is a name for the male; which is also called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tayosN","text_ar":"تَيْسٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", when he has become what is termed a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vaniY~","text_ar":"ثَنِىّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[q. v.], which he continues to be termed until he dies: (AHát, Msb, TA:) the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"female"},{"kind":"text","text":"is called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ZaboyapN","text_ar":"ظَبْيَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (AHát, T, M, Msb, K, TA,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EanozN","text_ar":"عَنْزٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maAEizapN","text_ar":"مَاعِزَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (AHát, Msb, TA:) the dual is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ZaboyaAni","text_ar":"ظَبْيَانِ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Msb, TA:) and the pl. is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aZobK","text_ar":"اَظْبٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, M, Msb, K,) originally"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aZobuYN","text_ar":"اَظْبُىٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Msb,) a pl. of pauc., (S,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ZubiY~N","text_ar":"ظُبِىٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ZibaA='u","text_ar":"ظِبَا=ءُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, M, Msb, K,) which last is of the masc. and fem., (M, Msb,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ZabayaAtN","text_ar":"ظَبَيَاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, M, Msb, K,) which is of the fem. (M, Msb.) One says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bihi","text_ar":"بِهِ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"daA='u ZaboYK","text_ar":"دَا=ءُ ظَبْىٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[lit."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"In him is the disease of a gazelle"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in him is no disease;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as there is [said to be] no disease in the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ZbY","text_ar":"ظبى"},{"kind":"text","text":". (AA, T.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laka","text_ar":"لَكَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EinodiY miAy^apN sin~a AlZ~aboYi","text_ar":"عِنْدِى مِايَةٌ سِنَّ الظَّبْىِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"To thee I owe a hundred"},{"kind":"text","text":"camels"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the age of the gazelle"},{"kind":"text","text":"], i. e., all of them"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vunoyaAn","text_ar":"ثُنْيَان"},{"kind":"text","text":"[pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vaniY~N","text_ar":"ثَنِىٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", q. v.], because the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ZbY","text_ar":"ظبى"},{"kind":"text","text":"does not exceed what is termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_ivonaA='N","text_ar":"اـِثْنَا=ءٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (M.) [See also a verse cited voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sin~N","text_ar":"سِنٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; in which the phrase"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fajaA='ato kasin~i AlZ~aboYi","text_ar":"فَجَا=ءَتْ كَسِنِّ الظَّبْىِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"And they came; like the age of the gazelle"},{"kind":"text","text":"was the age of every one of them.] It is said in a prov., ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laA^atorukan~ahu taroka ZubaY~K","text_ar":"لَاَتْرُكَنَّهُ تَرْكَ ظُبَىٍّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Zil~ahu","text_ar":"ظِلَّهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I will assuredly forsake him as a little gazelle forsakes the place of its shade"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; because the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ZbY","text_ar":"ظبى"},{"kind":"text","text":", when it leaves its covert, does not return to it: it is said in confirming the relinquishing of anything. (T. [See"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Zil~N","text_ar":"ظِلٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", where other relations of this prov. are mentioned.]) And in another prov.,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlZ~ibaA='a","text_ar":"الظِّبَا=ءَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EalaY Albaqari","text_ar":"عَلَى البَقَرِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", said when the tie of relationship and friendship between two men is severed, and it was used in the Time of Ignorance as a form of divorce:"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlZbA'","text_ar":"الظباء"},{"kind":"text","text":"is in the accus. case by reason of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aixotarotu","text_ar":"اِخْتَرْتُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AixotaAra","text_ar":"اِخْتَارَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", understood, [so that the meaning is I have preferred, or he has preferred,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the gazelles to the"},{"kind":"text","text":"wild"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"cows,"},{"kind":"text","text":"] by the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bqr","text_ar":"بقر"},{"kind":"text","text":"being meant the women: whence the saying,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaA='a yajur~u baqarahu","text_ar":"جَا=ءَ يَجُرُّ بَقَرَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[expl. in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bqr","text_ar":"بقر"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (Meyd. [See also Freytag's Arab. Prov. ii. 61.]) And one says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^atayotuhu Hiyna","text_ar":"اَتَيْتُهُ حِينَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$ad~a AlZ~aboYa Zil~uhu","text_ar":"شَدَّ الظَّبْىَ ظِلُّهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e. ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I came to him when its shade"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"confined the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ZbY","text_ar":"ظبى"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"gazelle"},{"kind":"text","text":"] by reason of the vehemence of the heat: or, as some relate it,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hiyno na$ada AlZ~aboYu Zil~ahu","text_ar":"حِينْ نَشَدَ الظَّبْىُ ظِلَّهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Talabahu","text_ar":"طَلَبَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"when the gazelle sought its shade"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) And it is said in a trad.,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_i*aA A^atayotahumo faA@robiDo fiY daArihimo ZaboyFA","text_ar":"اـِذَا اَتَيْتَهُمْ فَا@رْبِضْ فِى دَارِهِمْ ظَبْيًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"[expl. voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rabaDa","text_ar":"رَبَضَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (T, TA.)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bihi laA biZaboYK","text_ar":"بِهِ لَا بِظَبْىٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, TA,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bihi laA biZaboYK A^aEofara","text_ar":"بِهِ لَا بِظَبْىٍ اَعْفَرَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", a prov., meaning May this accident befall"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"liyanozilo bihi h`*ihi AlHaAdivapu","text_ar":"لِيَنْزِلْ بِهِ هٰذِهِ الحَادِثَةُ"},{"kind":"text","text":",)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"not a white antelope,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Meyd,) is said on an occasion of rejoicing at another's affliction, (S, Meyd, TA,) by way of imprecation, i. e. may God make that which has befallen him to cleave to him. (S, TA. [See also Freytag's Arab. Prov. i. 148.]) ―         -b2-  ["},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlZ~ibaA='u","text_ar":"الظِّبَا=ءُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^awolaAdu AlZ~ibaA='i","text_ar":"اَوْلَادُ الظِّبَا=ءِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"are mentioned by Freytag as names of"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Certain stars:"},{"kind":"text","text":"in relation to the former of which he refers to Ideler's “ Unters. ” pp. 20-21; and in relation to the latter, to the same work p. 21.] ―         -b3-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlZ~aboYu","text_ar":"الظَّبْىُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is the name of"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A brand,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"mark made with a hot iron, peculiar to some of the Arabs."},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, K.)"}],"source_refs":["TA","Msb","S","M","K","Meyd"]},{"entry_id":"n27511","headword_ar":"ظُبَىٌّ","root":"ZbY","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ZaboYN","text_ar":"ظَبْىٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[of which it is the dim.]."}],"source_refs":[]}]}}